    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个零售业务的核心流程图。重点是订单管理，它得和库存系统联动，最后还要能回馈到客户忠诚度这块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以是从订单管理出发，先到库存，再到客户忠诚度？这三个节点是单向流转关系吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，单向的。订单管理触发库存检查或更新，然后库存的变动数据会用于计算客户积分或会员等级。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画出来：订单管理指向库存，库存再指向客户忠诚度。节点名我用英文标识方便后续对接系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，客户忠诚度那个节点，名字是不是太长了？而且我看你写的连接好像有点问题——订单管理和库存之间是不是少了箭头方向？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我检查一下……哦，确实，我刚才的描述是对的，但画的时候箭头方向可能没标清楚。客户忠诚度我缩写成Retail_CustomerLoyalty，你觉得可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，Retail_CustomerLoyalty没问题。箭头方向确认是订单管理→库存→客户忠诚度，这样逻辑就顺了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正。现在三个节点都是TB纵向布局，订单管理在最上，库存居中，客户忠诚度在最下，双向箭头都已改为单向。",
      "elements_involved": [
